de by UN Member States and suggested measures and actions needed to move the implementation forward. Many of these recommendations were included in the resolution.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/17-December-2019-Key-Recommendations-for-UNGA-Final.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Embed of 17-December-2019-Key-Recommendations-for-UNGA-Final.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-5d1e2a79-918c-4c91-8ee6-bad1442b0a91\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/17-December-2019-Key-Recommendations-for-UNGA-Final.pdf\">17-December-2019-Key-Recommendations-for-UNGA-Final<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/17-December-2019-Key-Recommendations-for-UNGA-Final.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-5d1e2a79-918c-4c91-8ee6-bad1442b0a91\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Alongside other like-minded organisations, we developed a set of key recommendations for the 2019 UN General Assembly Resolution on the Rights of the Child.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3629,"template":"","tags":[53,80,20],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Key Recommendations for the 2019 UNGA Resolution - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/key-recommendations-for-the-2019-unga-resolution\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Key Recommendations for the 2019 UNGA Reso